desc: You You is a team of Asian-Americans bringing the best Asian cooking secrets and ingredients to the world. Tea Seed Oil is our first product — a healthy, high-heat cooking oil that’s packed with antioxidants and doesn’t burn when you’re cooking with it. This is an everyday, low-cholesterol cooking oil you will love.

layout.text: ADD A HEALTHY TOUCH TO EVERY ASIAN DISH
You You’s Tea Seed Oil is 100% organic and contains many other bioactive components that help with anti-inflammation!
